{"title_page": "Atrangi Re", "text_new": "{{short description|2021 film by Aanand Rai}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=March 2020}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Atrangi Re\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| director       = [[Aanand L. Rai]]\n| producer       = {{ubl|[[Bhushan Kumar]]|[[Krishan Kumar (actor)|Krishan Kumar]]|[[Aanand L. Rai]]|[[Akshay Kumar]]}}\n| writer         = [[Himanshu Sharma]] (story, dialogues)<br>[[Irshad Kamil]] (lyrics)\n| cinematography = [[Pankaj Kumar (cinematographer)|Pankaj Kumar]]\n| starring       = {{ubl|[[Akshay Kumar]]|[[Dhanush]]|[[Sara Ali Khan]]}}\n| music          = [[A. R. Rahman]]\n| editing        = Hemal Kothari\n| studio         = {{ubl|[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]|[[Colour Yellow Productions]]|Cape of Good Films}}\n| released       = 12 February 2021<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/akshay-kumar-teams-sara-ali-khan-dhanush-atrangi-re-reveals-he-said-yes-it-10-minutes-503785|title=Akshay Kumar teams up with Sara Ali Khan & Dhanush for Atrangi Re; REVEALS he said yes to it in 10 minutes|website=PINKVILLA|language=en|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref>\n| runtime        = \n| language       = [[Hindi]]\n| budget         = \n| gross          = \n}}\n \n'''''Atrangi Re''''' is upcoming Indian [[romantic drama film]] directed by [[Aanand L. Rai]], which stars [[Akshay Kumar]], [[Dhanush]] and [[Sara Ali Khan]]. The movie is produced under the studios [[T-Series (company)|T-Series]], [[Colour Yellow Productions]] and Cape of Good Films.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news18.com/news/movies/akshay-kumar-signs-aanand-l-rais-atrangi-re-to-share-screen-space-with-sara-ali-khan-and-dhanush-2478935.html|title=Akshay Kumar Signs Aanand L Rai's Musical 'Atrangi Re', to Share Screen Space with Sara Ali Khan and Dhanush|website=News18|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref> It is Dhanush's third Hindi film,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/sara-ali-khan-to-star-with-akshay-kumar-and-dhanush-in-atrangi-re-shooting-starts-on-march-1-1641489-2020-01-30|title=Sara Ali Khan to star with Akshay Kumar and Dhanush in Atrangi Re. Shooting starts on March 1|date=2020-01-30|website=India Today|language=en|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref> and was announced on 30 January 2020 by trade analyst [[Taran Adarsh]] who shared the first looks.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news18.com/news/movies/akshay-kumar-signs-aanand-l-rais-atrangi-re-to-share-screen-space-with-sara-ali-khan-and-dhanush-2478935.html|title=Akshay Kumar Signs Aanand L Rai's Musical 'Atrangi Re', to Share Screen Space with Sara Ali Khan and Dhanush|website=News18|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref> The film is written by [[Himanshu Sharma]] with music composed by [[A. R. Rahman]] with lyrics penned by [[Irshad Kamil]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/entertainment/akshay-kumar-to-have-cameo-appearance-in-aanand-l-rais-atrangi-re-starring-sara-ali-khan-and-dhanush-7975261.html|title=Akshay Kumar to have cameo appearance in Aanand L Rai's Atrangi Re, starring Sara Ali Khan and Dhanush- Entertainment News, Firstpost|date=2020-01-30|website=Firstpost|language=en|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref> [[Principal photography]] begun on 5 March 2020 in [[Varanasi]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aninews.in/news/entertainment/bollywood/sara-akshay-dhanushs-atrangi-re-goes-on-floors20200305103642/|title=Sara, Akshay, Dhanush's 'Atrangi Re' goes on floors!|date=2020-03-05|website=ANI|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref> and it is scheduled for cinema release worldwide on [[Valentine's Day]] 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/atrangi-re-sara-ali-khan-pens-a-heartfelt-note-for-the-makers-says-i-cant-believe-my-luck/articleshow/73757152.cms|title='Atrangi re': Sara Ali Khan pens a heartfelt note for the makers; says 'I can\u2019t believe my luck' - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Akshay Kumar]] as Ayush Agarwal (Writer) \n* [[Dhanush]] as Himanshu Tyagi \n* [[Sara Ali Khan]] as Deepali Mehra \n* [[Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub]] as William D'Costa\n* [[Nimrat Kaur]] as Priyanka Arora\n\n==Music==\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = Atrangi Re\n| type         = Soundtrack\n| artist       = [[A. R. Rahman]]\n| cover        = [[T-Series]]\n| alt          = \n| released     = {{Start date|df=yes|2021|}}\n| recorded     = 2020\n| venue        = \n| studio       = [[Panchathan Record Inn and AM Studios]], [[Chennai]], A.R. Studios [[Mumbai]]\n| genre        = [[Indian folk music|folk-classical]], [[Feature film soundtrack]]\n|language      = [[Hindi]],  [[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n| length       = \n| label        = [[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]\n|producer      = [[A.R. Rahman]]\n| prev_title   = [[Dil Bechara]]\n| prev_year    = 2020\n| next_title   = [[Ponniyin Selvan (upcoming film)|Ponniyin Selvan]]\n| next_year    = 2021\n}}\n\n===Development===\nThe [[film score]] and soundtrack are composed by [[A. R. Rahman]] with lyrics penned by [[Irshad Kamil]]. The first track rendered by [[Shreya Ghoshal]], has been already been recorded.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/aanandlrai/status/1227686851206504448?s=09|title=Ek aur shaher ek aur gali...ek aur kahani. @arrahman @Irshad_Kamil #AtrangiRepic.twitter.com/gNWDuQcBZY|last=RAI|first=AANAND L.|date=2020-02-12|website=@aanandlrai|language=hi|access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref>. Film's soundtrack is based on [[Indian folk music|folk-classical]].<ref>{{Citation|title=Atrangi Re {{!}} Announcement {{!}} Aanand L Rai {{!}} AR Rahman {{!}} Akshay Kumar, Sara Ali Khan, Dhanush|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=STRdrqGWsYU|language=en|access-date=2020-03-15}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n \n==External links==\n* {{imdb title|tt9766332}}\n* [https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movie/atrangi-re/ Atrangi Re] on [[Bollywood Hungama]]\n\n[[Category:202